c: 3
v: 118
t: "ya 'ayuha aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bishareihi, la tatakhidhuu alkafirin 'awlia' min dun almuminina, tutlewnhm ealaa 'asrarikim, fahula' la yafturwn ean 'iifsad halikim, wahum yafrahun bima yusibakum min darar wamakruha, waqad zaharat shidat albaghad fi kalamihim, wama tukhfi suduruhum min aleadawat lakum 'akbar wa'aezama. qad byanna lakum albarahin walhajja, litataeazau watahdhiruu، 'iin kuntum taeqilun ean allah mawaeizah wa'amruh wanahiha"